did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY

did.abstract: Correspondence, photographs, clippings, and biographical data concerning Cornell faculty, staff, and various other notables.

scopecontent.p: Correspondence, photographs, clippings, and biographical data concerning Cornell faculty, staff, and various other notables.
